**Favorite Movies & TV Shows App**

This project is a simple web application that allows you to create and manage a personal list of your favorite movies and TV shows.
You can add, edit, and delete entries, and movies are ordered by the rating you give them.


Features

Add your favorite movies or TV shows
View detailed information and cover images fetched from The Movie Database (TMDb)
Sort your list by the ratings you assign
Edit or delete any entry you make

Prerequisites
You will need to set up a .env file in the root directory with your API keys. Sign up for a free account at The Movie Database (TMDb) to get your API key.

.env Setup: Create a .env file and add the following variables with your TMDb API keys and the folling details:
MOVIE_DB_API_KEY=""
API_KEY=""
MOVIE_DB_SEARCH_URL="https://api.themoviedb.org/3/search/movie"
MOVIE_DB_IMAGE_URL="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500"
MOVIE_SEARCH_URL="https://api.themoviedb.org/3/movie/"

Usage
Add Movie/TV Show: Use the search function to find a movie or TV show from TMDb, and add it to your list.
Rate & Sort: Rate each movie or show, and your list will automatically be sorted by the rating.
Edit/Delete Entries: Click on any entry to modify or remove it from your list.

Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML + CSS 
Backend: Flask
API: The Movie Database (TMDb)
